message.text:
Walang pera? Walang problema! 

Dito, hindi lang numbers ang pinag-uusapan — TRUST, TRANSPARENCY, at DISKARTE ang puhunan. We make sure every project has a solid budget, every peso counts, and every fund is wisely allocated to benefit everyone.

No experience? Don’t worry! We’ll teach you how to:
- Create budget proposals
- Negotiate with sellers and suppliers
- Manage financial reports

JOIN FINANCE DIVISION!

Pero teka, paano naman kung mahilig ka sa connections? 

Kung gusto niyo mag-build ng strong partnerships, tara na sa Sponsorship Division! Here, we forge stronger ties with industry partners in the pursuit of providing quality service for our student body.

Learn more about:
- Drafting of Proposals
- Negotiation Techniques
- Networking

JOIN SPONSORSHIP DIVISION!

Apply now and be part of FEU IABF SC!

message.text:
Walang pera? Walang problema! 

Dito, hindi lang numbers ang pinag-uusapan — TRUST, TRANSPARENCY, at DISKARTE ang puhunan. We make sure every project has a solid budget, every peso counts, and every fund is wisely allocated to benefit everyone.

No experience? Don’t worry! We’ll teach you how to:
- Create budget proposals
- Negotiate with sellers and suppliers
- Manage financial reports

JOIN FINANCE DIVISION!

Pero teka, paano naman kung mahilig ka sa connections? 

Kung gusto niyo mag-build ng strong partnerships, tara na sa Sponsorship Division! Here, we forge stronger ties with industry partners in the pursuit of providing quality service for our student body.

Learn more about:
- Drafting of Proposals
- Negotiation Techniques
- Networking

JOIN SPONSORSHIP DIVISION!

Apply now and be part of FEU IABF SC!
